:0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:03:29.000Z","msg":"其實共匪套路，一向都係分化孤立，再慢慢秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n只要香港人齊心，唔分化唔割席。前線要小心行事，勿予對家口實，後援要相信支撐前線，且努力打民意戰，將打擊面集中柒婆同黑警濫權身上。<br />\n<br />\n咁香港其實重有得救。"},{"pid":"ba255814f1062f6bcee8a35bf4a30afae8994873","tid":1280094,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:04:01.000Z","msg":"咁撚叻跟左習種去面對美國人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6ccc9c9dea4c67c6cdd5bd51602620216dd8c5","tid":1280094,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba255814f1062f6bcee8a35bf4a30afae8994873","tid":1280094,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:04:01.000Z","msg":"咁撚叻跟左習種去面對美國人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:04:34.000Z","msg":"又捉緊棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08419d343e97a3f69c85a34835b575c5152217c2","tid":1280094,"uid":37918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:06:55.000Z","msg":"支那仔識閪治國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />權鬥貪污就叻"},{"pid":"c7430e078e4e31a670feab027ecfac827fb7669c","tid":1280094,"uid":113902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"其實咁大個政府 搵到個謀士諗到野唔難 唔信中國有高層插手 反而係7婆失勢就真 佢明明係一直都唔聽人講 要面既人 咁樣變法 証明都唔到佢話事<br />\n<br />\n利申 9up"},{"pid":"7f346e4cfee207cf6a6ae43b0b862e01c68c1b53","tid":1280094,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔信佢有南下<br />\n但現今科技咁發達，佢又唔係直接黎香港，係深圳同留係北京指揮有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fbbda8b165dd7fa206940179fa5